      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uniqlo-operator-fast-retailing-says-q2-profit-rose-72-2024-04-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 06:22:20 GMT</pubDate>
